            The European Community must take up the cause to untie aid, and put pressure on member countries to do so. Their credibility as donors will be severely undermined if they do not end this commercial self-interest. Will the Minister assure us that the matter is being looked into, and that the European Union&#x2014;like his own Government&#x2014;has stopped the practice of tying aid?
          </p>
